Description:
    Creates the minimum requirements for managed person model

Example:
    rails generate shortline:person

    This will create:
        # app/models/person.rb
        # app/models/concerns/auto_sluggable.rb
        # app/views/admin/people/_form.html.erb
        # app/views/admin/people/_show.html.erb
        # db/migrate/###########_create_people.rb
